Package: radish
Type: Package
Title: Fast gradient-based optimization of resistance surfaces
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2020-05-05
Author: Nathaniel S. Pope
Maintainer: Nathaniel S. Pope <nspope@utexas.edu>
Description: Maximum likelihood estimation for parameterized conductance models via Newton and quasi-Newton methods, for moderate-sized problems (e.g. rasters with less than a million cells)
License: MIT
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.4), raster, numDeriv, Matrix, nlme, corMLPE, MASS
Depends: Matrix
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
